| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3531 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3a81bace-a3ec-5e23-92dd-b80fa8d80395"
